				<!-- Main -->
					<div id="main">

						<!-- Intro -->
							<article id="work" style="text-align:center;font-size:20px">
								<h2 class="major">Work</h2>
								<span><a style="text-decoration: none" href="http://www.vetfetch.io"><img src="images/newVet.png"/></a></span>

								<p style="text-align:left">vetFetch is a site for users to manage their pets' health online. From design to production, we've partnered with vetFetch to launch their pet management software.<br />
								<p style="text-align:left">The initial release of the app will let users upload documents, file insurance claims, and track medical records for pets. vetFetch is currently seeking a seed round of venture funding.</p>

								<span><a style="text-decoration:none" href="http://www.dcanterwines.com"><img src="images/newDcanter.png"/></a></span>
								<p style="text-align:left">Brix&trade; by DcanterWines is logistics management software designed to streamline sales and delivery operations. Our team collaborated with Dcanter to architect their information systems and integrate legacy tools.</p>
								<p style="text-align:left">Today, Brix consolidates the functions of 4 off-the-shelf platforms into a single web application, reducing the time to curate, bill, and deliver orders to clients. As Dcanterwines continues to expand, we've laid the groundwork with light, adaptable software to meet its evolviing business requirements.</p>

								<span><a href="http://www.ambientsun.club"><img src="images/newAmbient.png"/></a></span>
								<p style="text-align:left">Ambient Sun Records came to us to modernize their web presence. We helped them implement their design, register the domain, and currently maintain the website.</p>
								<p style="text-align:left">The new site is a responsive single-page web application that captures user subscriptions. This landing page is an example of short-term projects we build for small businesses.</p>
							</article>

						<!-- About -->
							<article id="about" style="text-align:left;font-size:20px">
								<h2 class="major">Services</h2>
								<p>At Milkshake, our mission is to empower small businesses and startups to scale. We believe the best way to grow is by optimizing operations with technology. To help your company scale, we'll build software to address your specific needs.
								<p>Our clients rely for our expertise in 3 areas: consumer applications, custom business software, and landing pages. Please contact us for additional information about our rates.</p>
								<h2 class="major" style="text-align:center">About Us</h2>
								<p>We're Brooklyn-based developers programming with the latest technologies: React, React Native, and Node, to develop web and mobile apps for consumers and businesses.</p>
							</article>

						<!-- Contact -->
							<article id="contact">
								<h2 class="major">Contact</h2>
								<form method="post" action="api/inquiry">
									<div class="field half first">
										<label for="name">Name</label>
										<input type="text" name="name" id="name" />
									</div>
									<div class="field half">
										<label for="email">Email</label>
										<input type="text" name="email" id="email" />
									</div>
									<div class="field">
										<label for="message">Message</label>
										<textarea name="message" id="message" rows="4"></textarea>
									</div>
									<ul class="actions">
										<li><input type="submit" value="Send Message" class="special" /></li>
										<li><input type="reset" value="Reset" /></li>
									</ul>
								</form>
								<ul class="icons">
									<li><a href="https://twitter.com/milkshaketech" class="icon fa-twitter"><span class="label">Twitter</span></a></li>
									<li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/milkshakenyc/" class="icon fa-instagram"><span class="label">Instagram</span></a></li>
								</ul>
							</article>
					</div>

